  <brief_title>Fistulotomy With or Without Marsupialization for Treatment of Simple Anal Fistula</brief_title>
  <official_title>Fistuolotomy With or Without Marsupialization for Treatment of Simple Anal Fistula: a Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
