  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients with simple anal fistula will undergo fistulotomy operation and will be divided into
      two groups: the first will undergo marsupialization of the laid open fistula track and second
      group will not undergo marsupialization. The effect of marsupialization on healing of anal
      fistula will be compared postoperatively.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
